[{"question":"Why do you think you\u0027ve been able to inspire that kind of loyalty?","answer":"I am the wrong person to ask.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":35,"aSentId":36},{"question":"What do you work on other than making great music, but in terms of your relationship with an audience, what do you work on you think that brings you that extra time?","answer":"The truth.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":43,"aSentId":44},{"question":"As someone who\u0027d always been in the background like you say, the moment you went center stage, did you in that moment realize, wow, OK, this is what it\u0027s all about?","answer":"No, no.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":73,"aSentId":74},{"question":"Did you that night?","answer":"Yes, yes, I did.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":85,"aSentId":86},{"question":"But when you got that reaction from the crowd, and that was the first time you\u0027d had it, what was the experience like to you?","answer":"It was like floating.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":90,"aSentId":91},{"question":"What\u0027s the answer in your case?","answer":"Well, for me, I kind of knock me over.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":116,"aSentId":117},{"question":"Wouldn\u0027t you think that fame would be the greatest thing to happen to a person, you know?","answer":"Well, I think that everyone who\u0027s not famous assumes it is the greatest thing that could happen.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":120,"aSentId":121},{"question":"-- whoa, how\u0027s she handle this, you know?","answer":"And yet the fact that you mentor the acts on \"Idol,\" you\u0027ve done it a couple of times --","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":143,"aSentId":144},{"question":"If you\u0027re concerned about what may happen?","answer":"I would do that every day if I could.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":148,"aSentId":149},{"question":"Or is it just a pain in the backside?","answer":"I don\u0027t think of myself as being famous.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":160,"aSentId":161},{"question":"Have you met anybody in the last 20 years who didn\u0027t know who you were?","answer":"Well, yes, sure.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":174,"aSentId":175},{"question":"But not often?","answer":"But not often, no.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":177,"aSentId":178},{"question":"How much of it has she brought on herself?","answer":"I just remember them just driving her crazy.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":194,"aSentId":195},{"question":"Does it worry you that we\u0027re going to see more of that with people who just may be off psychologically, a little flawed anyway?","answer":"I do.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":208,"aSentId":209},{"question":"It\u0027s a drug, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"It\u0027s a drug.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":212,"aSentId":213},{"question":"That\u0027s what happens, right?","answer":"Well, on that bombshell, we are going to take a quick break so the audience can recover.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":220,"aSentId":221},{"question":"What advice would you give that Barry Manilow?","answer":"It\u0027s -- just stick to your guns.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":239,"aSentId":240},{"question":"Who\u0027s they?","answer":"Everybody but the audiences.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":242,"aSentId":243},{"question":"ORGAN: What was that like for you?","answer":"Well, it was dreadful.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":256,"aSentId":257},{"question":"Did I say something about our noses?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":267,"aSentId":268},{"question":"You know the concord hooter arrives, you know?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":280,"aSentId":281},{"question":"Are you a vain man, would you say?","answer":"I\u0027m as vain as the next guy.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":297,"aSentId":298},{"question":"Probably more so now, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"But only with you or with people like you who remind me I\u0027m not the average guy.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":307,"aSentId":308},{"question":"I say hello to the people out there and that\u0027s it, you know?","answer":"The average guy isn\u0027t earning stratospheric sums of money being a huge headline act in Vegas.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":311,"aSentId":312},{"question":"Where did it go?","answer":"I had hired a -- my first business manager.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":318,"aSentId":319},{"question":"Since that experience, did you get wiser about money?","answer":"I did.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":331,"aSentId":332},{"question":"Do I know how much I\u0027m worth?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":335,"aSentId":336},{"question":"That\u0027s sad though, isn\u0027t it?","answer":"You know, I thought so.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":360,"aSentId":361},{"question":"You remember that one?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":364,"aSentId":365},{"question":"I mean, I think that it would work again today, don\u0027t you?","answer":"So do I.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":371,"aSentId":372},{"question":"How would you feel ideologically, if McDonald\u0027s came to you now and said, would you front a commercial for us?","answer":"Oh, I would love it.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":374,"aSentId":375},{"question":"But the reason I -- the reason I was dwelling on the sad songs and the heartbreak was that you\u0027re quite private bloke, aren\u0027t you?","answer":"I am.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":402,"aSentId":403},{"question":"Had your heart broken?","answer":"Never.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":405,"aSentId":406},{"question":"Never?","answer":"Never.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":407,"aSentId":408},{"question":"Seriously?","answer":"Yes, never.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":409,"aSentId":410},{"question":"You\u0027ve never ever been in love or had your heartbroken?","answer":"I\u0027ve been in love, but I -- I\u0027m lucky enough never to have my heart broken.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":414,"aSentId":415},{"question":"How have you avoided what\u0027s struck everybody else?","answer":"Shoot, Piers, I don\u0027t know.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":422,"aSentId":423},{"question":"What\u0027s the definition of romance?","answer":"I guess, it\u0027s whatever -- I think romance, and love for that sake, is whatever anybody wants it to be.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":436,"aSentId":437},{"question":"For anybody in the fame game, is it sensible to open your book up like that, do you think?","answer":"For them, it might be wonderful for them.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":479,"aSentId":480},{"question":"Am I?","answer":"Yes, but the old mystique from celebrity -- the star game used to be everyone was on a plinth and you didn\u0027t really know much about them.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":489,"aSentId":490},{"question":"How do you come up with them?","answer":"The best ones that I\u0027ve come up with are not at the piano, when I\u0027m walking around.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":549,"aSentId":550},{"question":"When you do something like \"Mandy,\" where did that come to you?","answer":"You know I didn\u0027t write \"Mandy.\"","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":555,"aSentId":556},{"question":"\"If I Should Love Again,\" how did you come up with that?","answer":"\"If I Should Love Again\" was a --","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":560,"aSentId":561},{"question":"Was she one of the greatest showman you have played with?","answer":"Oh, absolutely.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":602,"aSentId":603},{"question":"She says is there anyone you have met that really made you feel star struck?","answer":"ANILOW: Yeah, Annie Lennox.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":630,"aSentId":631},{"question":"Isn\u0027t that amazing?","answer":"It is amazing.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":649,"aSentId":650},{"question":"Quite interesting, what would you be doing if you hadn\u0027t gone into music, do you think?","answer":"I can\u0027t imagine myself not --","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":669,"aSentId":670},{"question":"Do you ever wonder?","answer":"I would have been playing in some bar at night, complaining about how nobody understands me.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":671,"aSentId":672},{"question":"How do you feel about that?","answer":"I\u0027ve never heard of that one, I must say.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":699,"aSentId":700},{"question":"That there was one of my songs?","answer":"\"Let\u0027s Hang on.\"","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":703,"aSentId":704},{"question":"Really?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":729,"aSentId":730},{"question":"When you say wrote in a dream, do you actually mean these things come to you sometimes in dreams?","answer":"Well, this one did, yeah.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":742,"aSentId":743},{"question":"Do you wake up?","answer":"This one woke me up.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":746,"aSentId":747},{"question":"Do you jump out of bed and write it all down?","answer":"I did.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":761,"aSentId":762},{"question":"Who of the modern crop catches your eye?","answer":"The modern crop.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":774,"aSentId":775},{"question":"Any other?","answer":"Well, I like Sting\u0027s work.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":776,"aSentId":777},{"question":"Do you really think I\u0027m going to tell you that?","answer":"Yes.","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":784,"aSentId":785},{"question":"What is the song that you literally can\u0027t hear anymore?","answer":"I would never answer that question!","docId":"110623pmt","qSentId":789,"aSentId":790}]